A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a glowing modular machine being assembled by mechanical arms in a neon-lit workshop. The central device resembles a sleek, futuristic cube with multiple glowing slots and ports, where smaller luminescent geometric modules are being inserted like puzzle pieces. Electric blue and magenta energy pulses flow through transparent tubes connecting the components. The scene is set in a dark industrial space with holographic interface panels floating nearby, casting colored light reflections on wet metallic surfaces. Steam rises from cooling vents, and intricate circuit patterns glow beneath glass floor panels. The atmosphere suggests unauthorized tinkering and creative modification, with tools scattered around and spare glowing components stacked in the background.
